comments: Nesmith's (IND) forearm momentarily brushes Antetokounmpo's (MIL) front as he aligns alongside the offensive player's path and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Nesmith (IND) is retreating in Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path when he jumps into the air and absorbs the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt at the basket.
Turner (IND) firms up over his left leg and marginal contact occurs as Beasley (MIL) attempts to defend over the pick.
Lopez (MIL) leans into Turner's (IND) space and initiates contact that affects Turner's FOM.
Beasley (MIL) momentarily brings his hand around Haliburton's (IND) left arm and the marginal contact dissolves as Haliburton receives the handoff.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Beasley's (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Haliburton (IND) establishes a right pivot foot and releases the ball to start his dribble prior to lifting and re-planting his foot.
Lopez (MIL) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal brush contact occurs with Haliburton's (IND) arm at the start of his dribble.
Turner (IND) brings his hands toward Beasley (MIL) and marginal contact occurs as Turner releases away to roll.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) and Turner (IND) come together at the same spot on the floor and the contact is marginal.
Lillard (MIL) steps toward the basket and marginal contact occurs as he comes together with Brown (IND) during the inbound.
Haliburton (IND) deflects the pass prior to incidental arm contact occurring with Beasley (MIL).
Hield's (IND) hand momentarily brushes Middleton's (MIL) front during the drive and the contact is marginal.
Hield (IND) removes his hand from Middleton's (MIL) side during the driving shot attempt in the paint and the touch is marginal.
Beasley (MIL) commits a take foul on Brown (IND). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Turner's (IND) forearm grazes Beasley's (MIL) side during the driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Haliburton (IND) rests his forearm on Beasley's (MIL) side and removes the marginal contact after Beasley's gather into the driving shot attempt.
Lillard (MIL) commits a take foul on Brown (IND). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Middleton (MIL) and Hield (IND) engage and disengage as the screen is set and the contact is marginal.
Lopez (MIL) firms up in Brown's (IND) path and his arms brush Brown's front as he moves around the screen. The contact on the play is marginal.
Hield's (IND) hand grazes Middleton's (MIL) midsection during the jump shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Hield (IND). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Turner (IND) does not make contact with the ball during his legal contest of Middleton's (MIL) driving shot attempt.
Hield (IND) releases the ball prior to his foot coming down out of bounds.
